THIS IS THE SAME MAP AS GG_AS_DUST, BUT SOME GUYS COMPLAIN ABOUT IT THAT IT WASNT AIM + BUYZONES.





i was tired of the dev textures so i decided to make a dust theme.

- each team got a buyzone.
- this map has 15 spawnpoints for each teams.
- u can't go on roofs.
- I used de_Dust2 3D skybox
- and the doors of de_dust2
- So thanks to valve.

- Special thanks to idemon and itachi for map testing.

- Do not decompile this map without my permission
- this map is supported by Azzshot.org.ru

Mathijs.
